Localization.Name: Roussimoff Rehabilitation Systems
Localization.Description: Roussimoff Rehabilitation Systems (RRS) is an Earth-based corporation that provides rehabilitation services, personal body armor and defensive systems throughout the UEE. Their arms division is responsible for a groundbreaking series of new weaponry designed to incapacitate opponents without taking lives.

Localization.Name: Morozov-SH-I Core Lifeforce
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Armor
Damage Reduction: 40%
Temp. Rating: -75 / 105 °C
Radiation Protection: 26800 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 12K µSCU
Backpacks: All

Featuring the same fortified armor plating, special anti-rip protective padding and ample storage, as the Morozov SH, the SH-I industrial variant was designed by RRS to protect workers employed in hostile zones while ensuring they had the full range of motion required to perform their duties. The Lifeforce edition was designed with first responders in mind with a highly visible white, red, and grey color scheme.
